{"type": "article", "id": 55768, "title": "这款概念洗衣机，可以衣服鞋子一起洗｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-30T23:21:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52252, "name": "±0"}, {"id": 52253, "name": "Rosendahl Copenhagen"}, {"id": 52254, "name": "Bubble Lab"}, {"id": 2634, "name": "Under Armour"}, {"id": 24722, "name": "JBL"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 52255, "name": "Kazushige Miyake"}, {"id": 52256, "name": "Daisuke Ishigami"}, {"id": 52257, "name": "Steen Christiansen"}, {"id": 52258, "name": "Erling Andersen"}, {"id": 42616, "name": "Dwayne Johnson"}, {"id": 47123, "name": "Noé Duchaufour Lawrance"}, {"id": 52259, "name": "Ji Eun Oh"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 177, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180730205113if2M6kTapEO8PGnA.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s9 {font-kerning: none; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>3 Space Washing Machine by Ji Eun Oh</h3><p>洗衣机现在已经成了很多人家中的必备电器，解决了洗衣难题，但刷鞋子，还是一件耗时耗力的事儿。设计师 Ji Eun Oh 最近推出了一款名为 3 Space 的概念洗衣机，允许你将运动鞋扔进洗衣机，帮你刷鞋。</p><p>3 Space 允许同时清洗衣物和鞋子，衣服放在上面的滚筒里，鞋子放在下面的抽屉，两者可以同步清洗，不必担心水会相互污染。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205141OlTsbAP1LnFWGfRQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205141eSz31rdAIoHy0nYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205142zhQSCFy56bI4Dj0R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205142wqMmID7Cc32dgeNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205142eAroquXvPU79xibz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205142mOWDYN2p1PthIZ85.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/07/29/clean-kicks-and-clothes-at-once/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Harp Sofa by Noé Duchaufour Lawrance fou Zaozuo</h3><p>巴黎设计师 Noé Duchaufour Lawrance 以其“自然的、有机的、有着流动性结构状态”的设计而闻名。最近，他为家居设计品牌造作设计了新款竖琴沙发，灵感源自竖琴音乐，勾画琴线融于沙发，以实木结构立体呈现。</p><p>沙发框架由白蜡木制成，结合分段拼合无缝成型，呈现通体连贯的优美流线，再以哑光漆面效果呈现。茶白格、抹绿格两色面料，选用 100％澳大利亚进口纯羊毛织造，耐磨耐脏，兼备抗皱抗菌的耐久性。售价 14999 元起，<a href=\"https://www.zaozuo.com/item/300230\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205225vKbLioug86wFhXte.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205225ieJDqH1of4CBAk60.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205226pvwHlyEXnFN1qBVx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205229U4TaVP3OH0QywI2S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205230X0wF6hAN93y8KJEU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205230REbkZVYGH3ziKUga.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205231BGz5VC0AmROarEWP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Project Rock by Under Armour x Dwayne Johnson x JBL</h3><p>运动品牌 Under Armour 与 Dwayne “The Rock” Johnson 携手，联合耳机制造商 JBL，推出全新 Project Rock 运动无线头戴式训练耳机。</p><p>新作的外观设计线条硬朗，通过 Johnson 在高强度训练中的严格穿戴测试，专为健身爱好者训练定制。耳机配备了较大尺寸的按钮便于寻找，让使用者在锻炼过程中更易操作。</p><p>每次充满电后续航时间长达 16 小时，可满足一周的运动需求，此外只需充电五分钟，便可播放一小时。售价 2099 元，<a href=\"https://www.underarmour.cn/p1325450-001#LP|JBLROCK|S1|JBLROCK|JBLROCK|2018072\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205351mE7ujGypweKsfZSl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205351yXh1GKNBpqPLef5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205352oPJxmA8S3MYkZtyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205352ShtX564nHfxZ2YFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205352A2cuvi9VJ4EBn6wm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205352lvkbLcr1AsCZY9ai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.underarmour.cn/p1325450-001#LP|JBLROCK|S1|JBLROCK|JBLROCK|2018072\" rel=\"nofollow\">Under Armour</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Drip by Bubble Lab</h3><p>创新厂商 Bubble Lab 舍弃机器手臂复杂、高成本的设计，推出一款简易版自动咖啡冲泡机器 Drip，可以更灵活地冲泡手冲咖啡，出发点很简单，就是要让每一杯咖啡的冲泡品质都是一样的，减少人为不可控因素。</p><p>不使用时，Drip 手冲咖啡机可以埋在桌子底下，需要使用时只要通过智能手表或是手机便可遥控它，自动启动，接着把咖啡杯放在特定位置，然后启动，就可以看到它用非常固定的频率和方向，流出水流来冲泡咖啡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205428nDzPhafxy7i3MNqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205429TIKZBDWpRbH7lSkr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205432plEjRod2NQ3X0MeD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205433dVJmTQr6h1IXeUFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205434k5e9b2oxly1U6dSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205435lr9QNpDWUC35I4vX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205434visFpzql5dY8mCr2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.528125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.bubblelab.com/drip\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bubble Lab</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Picto Wall Clock by Steen Christiansen &amp; Erling Andersen for Rosendahl Copenhagen</h3><p>丹麦生活方式品牌 Rosendahl Copenhagen 推出新作 Picto 挂钟，试图用最简单的方式传递俏皮的情绪。</p><p>Picto 带有一丝复古意味，与斯堪的纳维亚 20 世纪中期的图标设计相呼应。它提供多种颜色组合，包括黑白、橙灰等。与传统的挂钟不同，Picto 的设计并没有精确的秒针，仅提供分钟和小时信息，其中时针是位于钟面上的固定圆点，另有一条短线代表分针。操刀设计的是 Steen Christiansen 和Erling Andersen，很克制，带来的是极简现代的美学风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205517PFD56bG0HZwWEBXO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205517aw6Kto3zOQiVWTym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205517iwUpTsQ9c45z2Bey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205517iENC3uLWeKv5aTXH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205518f9K4yzUjJOtCg0wH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807302055170ivWAesLgw3uoJXy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://minimalissimo.com/picto-wall-clock/\" rel=\"nofollow\">minimalissimo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Miyake Suitcase by Kazushige Miyake &amp; Daisuke Ishigami for Plus Minus Zero (±0)</h3><p>日本家电品牌 ±0 推出一款新的行李箱 Miyake，出自设计师 Kazushige Miyake 和 Daisuke Ishigami 之手。</p><p>这款行李箱的主要特点，是其简约利落的外壳形状和平滑饰面。设计师将箱体的不平整部分最小化，并且赋予了整个箱体单一的色彩。Miyake 行李箱提供三种不同的尺寸，另有黑、白、红三种颜色可供选择。</p><p>除了提供细致保护的铝制箱体框架之外，Miyake 行李箱特制的降噪脚轮，传递出一种柔和轻盈的感觉，这个细节很棒，避免我们在使用行李箱过程中制造太多噪音。售价 37800 日元，<a href=\"https://www.plusminuszero.jp/item/8269/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205604VGdy6ABjal0EHniw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205604zTi5Q1wZVnScsdOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807302056049e4WZx0tcl6yLTgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205605KJT0sEDch37LO9Ci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205604uF652K1htdCALreN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180730205605S0oKjWGgPrm7VTHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.plusminuszero.jp/item/8269/\" rel=\"nofollow\">±0</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}